\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The Ayramun erupted in laughter. Mandri didn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t laugh because the sight of that cool, crystal water being wasted on the sand brought his own great thirst into sudden, stark relief.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 If Obo was bothered by any of it, he did not show it, and when Ayram finished with his little show, he said, }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93If the girl can\u8217\'92t control you, then why haven\u8217\'92t you split me in half with Mazidfire?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Only my Minder can call forth the fire.\u8221\'94}
